snippet.title: NES Longplay [341] Castle of Dragon
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by JagOfTroy

Another game miserably ported from Arcade to the NES. I have never played the Arcade version so I am unable to compare the two but this was really an unpleasant experience overall. But.. there are so many games that are worse I guess. -
